#: 21337012-0-995
msgctxt "21337012-0-995"
msgid "Listen well and smell my words! The time draws near! "
"\n"
"\nThe ravenous rodent spoke to me. He said the Mad God walks among us. "
"\n"
"\nBring your offering and make your sacrifice, or the chateau will consume you!"
msgstr "この言葉をよく聞いてかみしめること！ 時が迫っている！\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n腹ぺこ鼠に言われた。マッドゴッドが紛れ込んでいると。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n生け贄を持って捧げに来ること。でなければ館の食い物になるのみ！"

