#: 21337012-0-990
msgctxt "21337012-0-990"
msgid "Mistress,"
"\n"
"\nWe know where he shall be. We will remove the foul Resolute from the battlefield. We shall return to the island tower when we have completed our task."
"\n"
"\nEver faithful, Jessen."
msgstr "主よ\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n彼の居場所は分かっています。忌々しい篤信者は戦場から取り除きます。仕事が完了したら島の塔に戻る予定です。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n忠実なるジェッセンより"

