msgid "Your instructions are simple. Follow Dimitri into Farangel's Delve and locate the abandoned fort therein. There should be ample amounts of supplies to take, which we can turn around and sell in Wayrest. We should turn a tidy profit. Do this for the Supernal Dreamers, and further our cause!"
